Tableau dashboard is a tool which helps us to visualize data by building interactive & sharable dashboard. It is user friendly.
Advantages of Tableau :
  Data visualization is so easy in tableau rather than in excel sheet  - helps us in providing better insights
  It helps us to create interactive visualizations
  Ease of implementation : Dont have to write complicated codes for creating those visualizations. can be done easily by dragging and dropping and with calculated fields
  
